OL,6,FKelly - who is using a fake name for
OL,7,Fanonymity - had fallen asleep on a
OL,8,FQatar Airways flight from Doha to
OL,9,FLondon Gatwick in September last year,
OL,10,Fwhen she was awoken by the man sitting
OL,11,Fnext to her with his hands down her
OL,12,Ftrousers.
OL,14,FKelly was 24 at the time of the
OL,15,Fattack. She would later find out she
OL,16,Fhad been assaulted by 66-year-old
OL,17,FMomade Jussab.
OL,19,F"It felt like a never-ending nightmare"
