OL,6,F"When I saw his hands, I tried to take
OL,7,Fthem off. I said to him, what are you
OL,8,Fdoing? I said, stop. He said, no,
OL,9,Fplease," Kelly told ITV News. "I tried
OL,10,Fto take his hands out of my trousers.
OL,11,FI used both hands forcefully."
OL,13,FFrightened and shaking, Kelly ran to
OL,14,Fthe aeroplane's bathroom. When she
OL,15,Fexplained to a flight attendant what
OL,16,Fhad happened, she was moved to a
OL,17,Fdifferent seat for the remaining two
OL,18,Fhours of the flight.
