OL,6,F"They moved me next to a couple who
OL,7,Fwere sleeping. I stayed up most of the
OL,8,Fflight. Anyone that walked past, I was
OL,9,Fscared, panicking," Kelly says.
OL,11,F"It felt like I was never going to
OL,12,Fleave the plane. Honestly, it felt
OL,13,Flike it was a never ending nightmare.
OL,15,F"I was just awake, staring into space,
OL,16,Fin shock, scared, looking at the
OL,17,Fcouple next to me, thinking maybe they
OL,18,Fwould do something. I was paranoid."
