OL,6,FJussab was arrested upon landing, and
OL,7,Fwas sentenced in May to six-and-a-half
OL,8,Fyears in prison, after being found
OL,9,Fguilty of one count of sexual assault
OL,10,Fby penetration and two counts of
OL,11,Fsexual assault.
OL,13,FBut because the assault took place on
OL,14,Fa plane not registered in Britain,
OL,15,FKelly has been told she does not
OL,16,Fqualify for compensation, a decision
OL,17,Fher lawyers say highlights a serious
OL,18,Foversight in the law.
OL,20,F"I just want help. I felt like I
OL,21,Fwasn't heard"
