OL,6,FKelly had applied for the government's
OL,7,FCriminal Injuries Compensation (CIC)
OL,8,FScheme, which provides financial
OL,9,Fcompensation to individuals who have
OL,10,Fbeen physically or mentally injured,
OL,11,For whose close relatives have died, as
OL,12,Fa result of violent crime in England,
OL,13,FScotland, and Wales.
OL,15,F"They rejected my application and they
OL,16,Fsaid that it wasn't in a relevant
OL,17,Fplace," says Kelly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
