OL,6,F"I appealed it and said that I'm a
OL,7,FBritish citizen. He was arrested in
OL,8,Fthe UK, tried in the UK, he's in a UK
OL,9,Fprison. I don't see why I should miss
OL,10,Fout on compensation just because it
OL,11,Fwasn't in the British aircraft. And
OL,12,Fthey rejected it again."
OL,14,FKelly says the experience has left her
OL,15,Fstruggling even more with poor mental
OL,16,Fhealth.
