OL,6,F"I felt like I wasn't heard. Honestly,
OL,7,Feven though I got justice, I still
OL,8,Fhave to go to therapy. There's only so
OL,9,Fmuch the NHS can do, and I want to see
OL,10,Fa psychiatrist.
OL,12,F"I know how bad my mental health is at
OL,13,Fthe moment. I know what I want to do.
OL,14,FI know that it requires money, money
OL,15,Fthat I don't have.
OL,17,F"I just want help and if I'm
OL,18,Fcompensated, I can feel I can get the
OL,19,Fhelp that I need."
