OL,6,FBut she says she feels the government
OL,7,Fdoesn't fully grasp the impact of her
OL,8,Fordeal.
OL,10,F"I don't think they understand the
OL,11,Fseverity of my case," she says.
OL,13,F"All they have said is, I'm sorry this
OL,14,Fhas happened to you, but it wasn't on
OL,15,Fa British controlled aircraft, so we
OL,16,Fcan't help you."
OL,18,F"A gap that needs closing urgently"
