OL,6,F"Our client was refused compensation
OL,7,Funder the Criminal Injuries
OL,8,FCompensation scheme simply because it
OL,9,Fwas a foreign flight and the rules
OL,10,Fhave not been amended in line with the
OL,11,Fupdates to the Civil Aviation Act,"
OL,12,Fsays Claire Powell, a solicitor at
OL,13,FLeigh Day.
OL,15,F"It is a gap that needs closing
OL,16,Furgently and we trust the Justice
OL,17,FSecretary will agree, particularly in
OL,18,Flight of this Government's commitment
OL,19,Fto addressing violence against women
OL,20,Fand girls."
